author: Source: Knutsford Guardian
title: David Schwimmer returns to Channel 4 in new sitcom - Knutsford Guardian
text:
In the six-part sitcom, David will star as an American producer brought in to save floundering breakfast TV show Good Morning with Gail Sinclair when it begins to haemorrhage viewers. Nighty Night star Julia Davis co-wrote the script with Nick Mohammed and will play the self-styled "Queen of Daytime TV", Gail Sinclair.
 Knutsford Guardian.
